thread.title: BRIEF-Motus GI Holdings Sees IPO Of 4.25 Mln Shares Of Common Stock Priced Between $5.00 - $7.00 Per Share

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Motus GI Holdings Sees IPO Of 4.25 Mln Shares Of Common Stock Priced Between $5.00 - $7.00 Per Share
text:
Jan 31 (Reuters) - Motus GI Holdings Inc:
* MOTUS GI HOLDINGS INC SEES IPO OF 4.25 MILLION SHARES OF COMMON STOCK PRICED BETWEEN $5.00 AND $7.00 PER SHARE - SEC FILING
* MOTUS GI HOLDINGS INC SAYS INTENDS TO USE ABOUT $8.0 MILLION OF IPO PROCEEDS FOR COMMERCIALIZATION ACTIVITIES RELATED TO OUR PURE-VU SYSTEM
* MOTUS GI HOLDINGS INC SAYS INTENDS TO USE ABOUT $8.0 MILLION OF IPO PROCEEDS FOR RESEARCH AND DEVELOPMENT ACTIVITIES, Source text: ( bit.ly/2DQtkWl ) Further company coverage:
